title: Week 15 Preview: Colts vs. Patriots, Ravens vs. Packers, and a Look at the Rest of the Slate
description:
Benjamin, Kaelen, and Steven begin their Week 15 Friday Walk Through by sharing their reactions to the Chiefs' Thursday night win over the Chargers.(1:40) Then they dissect the biggest matchups of the week, including Colts-Patriots, (10:07) Ravens-Packers (22:08), and highlight the Games That Need Games (35:46). Finally, they wrap everything up with Gimme a Reason, in which they deliver their takes on the rest of the Week 15 slate (54:17)
Hosts: Benjamin Solak, Kaelen Jones, Steven Ruiz
Production Assistant: Chris Sutton
Additional Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
